          <br>
          <p style="color: #9CDCFE;">// Windows 7 or earlier:</p>
          <p>Start → Programs → Accessories → Notepad</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 40px 0 20px;">Step 2: Write Your HTML</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Create a new file and write or paste your HTML code:</p>
      
