        <div class="window-header">
          <div class="window-btn red"></div>
          <div class="window-btn yellow"></div>
          <div class="window-btn green"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="window-body">
          <p><span style="color: #569CD6;">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span></p>
          <p><span style="color: #569CD6;">&lt;html&gt;</span></p>
          <p><span style="color: #569CD6;">&lt;body&gt;</span></p>
          <br>
          <p><span style="color: #569CD6;">&lt;h1&gt;</span>My First Heading<span style="color: #569CD6;">&lt;/h1&gt;</span></p>
          <p><span style="color: #569CD6;">&lt;p&gt;</span>My first paragraph.<span style="color: #569CD6;">&lt;/p&gt;</span></p>
          <br>
          <p><span style="color: #569CD6;">&lt;/body&gt;</span></p>
          <p><span style="color: #569CD6;">&lt;/html&gt;</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 40px 0 20px;">Step 3: Save Your HTML File</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Save the file with proper extension and encoding:</p>
      
      <div class="code-window">
        <div class="window-header">
          <div class="window-btn red"></div>
          <div class="window-btn yellow"></div>
          <div class="window-btn green"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="window-body">
          <p>File → Save As...</p>
          <p>Name: <span style="color: #CE9178;">"index.html"</span></p>
          <p>Save as type: <span style="color: #CE9178;">"All Files"</span></p>
          <p>Encoding: <span style="color: #CE9178;">"UTF-8"</span></p>
        </div>
