      <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Double-click your HTML file to open it in your default browser, or right-click and select "Open with" to choose a browser.</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 40px 0;">
        <svg width="300" height="200" viewBox="0 0 300 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
